♪Time and space brought me
to another yellowed page♪

30
00:01:25,470 --> 00:01:26,830
♪Sunlight pierces through♪

31
00:01:26,830 --> 00:01:28,560
♪One comes and goes as one pleases♪

32
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:30,140
♪My Go board holds both sides♪

33
00:01:30,140 --> 00:01:31,870
♪When I set the game, learn to see♪

34
00:01:31,870 --> 00:01:33,530
♪Don't be a sore loser♪

35
00:01:33,530 --> 00:01:35,010
♪So many lies and deceits♪

36
00:01:35,010 --> 00:01:36,890
♪I can see through every play♪

37
00:01:36,890 --> 00:01:38,440
♪May I live and die
with the sun♪

38
00:01:38,620 --> 00:01:41,180
=Guardians of the Dafeng=

39
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:44,140
=Episode 13=

40
00:01:44,390 --> 00:01:45,360
No. 3,

41
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,210
I can't believe you'd do this

42
00:01:47,830 --> 00:01:50,030
- for No. 6.
- I'd die for a bosom friend.

43
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:51,800
The words No. 6 said earlier were

44
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,110
touching and heart-rending,

45
00:01:53,110 --> 00:01:54,390
deafening and enlightening.

46
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:56,390
A righteous person like No. 6

47
00:01:56,390 --> 00:01:57,910
should not have been captured,

48
00:01:57,910 --> 00:02:01,310
nor should he have been tortured
by those Guardians.

49
00:02:02,310 --> 00:02:04,110
As a comrade of No. 6,

50
00:02:04,310 --> 00:02:06,910
these are things I should bear.

51
00:02:06,910 --> 00:02:07,750
Rest assured.

52
00:02:08,040 --> 00:02:09,670
Even if I die and my path is lost,

53
00:02:09,870 --> 00:02:12,080
I will have no regrets.

54
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:13,160
Well said.

55
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,640
(No. 1, No. 3, No. 4)
No. 3

56
00:02:14,640 --> 00:02:15,960
is truly a model for us all,

57
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:18,110
unlike No. 4,

58
00:02:18,110 --> 00:02:20,270
who often talks about morality,

59
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:22,110
but when real trouble comes,

60
00:02:22,110 --> 00:02:23,800
no one knows where he hides.

61
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:24,990
(No. 2)
Come on.

62
00:02:25,610 --> 00:02:26,480
Didn't I tell you?

63
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,920
I wasn't in the capital last night.

64
00:02:28,260 --> 00:02:29,800
What right do you have to condemn me?

65
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,760
Didn't you claim

66
00:02:31,110 --> 00:02:32,990
to be some Winged Woman?

67
00:02:33,830 --> 00:02:34,870
Don't you have wings?

68
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:35,990
Fly over and see.

69
00:02:35,990 --> 00:02:37,040
Fly over?

70
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:38,640
If I flew to the capital,

71
00:02:38,660 --> 00:02:40,390
I'd first go to Treasure Sect
and stab you.

72
00:02:40,390 --> 00:02:41,800
You just talk and do nothing.

73
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,360
I'm waiting for you, Little Wings.

74
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:45,830
Just wait. You really have a death wish.

75
00:02:45,830 --> 00:02:46,860
I'm right here.

76
00:02:46,860 --> 00:02:48,240
If you want to kill me, come here.

77
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,640
- Just wait.
- I'm waiting.

78
00:02:49,640 --> 00:02:50,480
Just wait.

79
00:02:54,940 --> 00:02:57,580
(Puppet)

80
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,670
Guangxiao, what's on your mind?

81
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,320
It must be a young lady.

82
00:03:03,990 --> 00:03:05,930
I heard you went to Haoqi Tower
again yesterday.

83
00:03:06,390 --> 00:03:09,110
I also heard you dismissed
Mr. Yang and Mr. Nangong.

84
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,670
Who told you that?

85
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:11,960
The people involved.

86
00:03:13,550 --> 00:03:15,520
Mr. Nangong
went to see the chief

87
00:03:15,590 --> 00:03:16,430
and cursed you

88
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:17,870
for four hours at Breeze Hall.

89
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,320
It looks like I won't be able to stay

90
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,040
at Breeze Hall for much longer.

91
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:28,090
Today, I'm going all out.

92
00:03:28,090 --> 00:03:30,360
(Guo's Bamboo Crafts)
Forget about the power and wealth.

93
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,150
I must express my feelings.

94
00:03:34,550 --> 00:03:37,150
Huaiqing is nothing but a hollow title,

95
00:03:37,270 --> 00:03:38,480
ruining people's futures.

96
00:03:38,550 --> 00:03:41,110
She drove me away for a new lover.

97
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:43,150
I really had no eyes

98
00:03:43,150 --> 00:03:45,390
to be deceived like this.

99
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:48,640
Huaiqing has wronged me.

100
00:03:48,990 --> 00:03:51,360
Huaiqing has wronged me.

101
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:53,550
I have been wronged.

102
00:03:53,550 --> 00:03:55,590
Huaiqing has wronged me.

103
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:58,390
She mentioned a millennium-old lingzhi
on the mountain,

104
00:03:58,390 --> 00:03:59,430
and I ate it.

105
00:03:59,670 --> 00:04:02,110
It blinded my eyes.

106
00:04:02,590 --> 00:04:05,360
Huaiqing has wronged me.

107
00:04:05,990 --> 00:04:10,200
Huaiqing has wronged me.

108
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,200
Huaiqing?

109
00:04:11,430 --> 00:04:12,480
A beggar,

110
00:04:13,430 --> 00:04:14,430
a prisoner,

111
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,270
and a blind physician

112
00:04:17,080 --> 00:04:20,200
will soon appear one after another
before Xu Qi'an

113
00:04:21,080 --> 00:04:23,470
to tell him about their tragic plight.

114
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:25,520
The reason for all this is simple:

115
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:30,880
Huaiqing has wronged me.

116
00:04:31,830 --> 00:04:35,000
Moreover, we have arranged everything
on this street.

117
00:04:35,150 --> 00:04:37,150
This will not spread,

118
00:04:37,230 --> 00:04:38,790
but it's enough to make Mr. Xu

119
00:04:39,270 --> 00:04:41,080
believe it.

120
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:44,030
This way,

121
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:47,390
Huaiqing's name will be enough
to scare off Xu Qi'an.

122
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:48,480
Then

123
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:50,390
I will reveal my identity

124
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:51,910
and try to win him over,

125
00:04:51,910 --> 00:04:53,390
showing I can forgive the past.

126
00:04:53,830 --> 00:04:55,200
He will surely think

127
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:58,120
I am magnanimous

128
00:04:58,830 --> 00:04:59,830
and will be

129
00:05:00,390 --> 00:05:02,760
deeply grateful to me.

130
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,830
Your Highness, how wise of you.

131
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,160
Your Highness.

132
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,770
Xu Qi'an is outside asking to see you.

133
00:05:17,470 --> 00:05:18,560
This is also fake?

134
00:05:18,790 --> 00:05:20,680
Aren't you blind now?

135
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:23,720
Kneel.

136
00:05:28,350 --> 00:05:29,470
What does this mean?

137
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,520
Your Highness,

138
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:33,390
this is simply horrifying.

139
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:37,200
I encountered
these sinister people today,

140
00:05:37,350 --> 00:05:40,270
and they maliciously
slandered you in public.

141
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,120
How absurd.

142
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,820
Your intentions
are worthy of punishment.

143
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:48,030
Xuan, take them down

144
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,560
for interrogation.

145
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,680
Let's see who's behind this.

146
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:52,200
- Hurry.
- Yes.

147
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:53,200
No need.

148
00:05:54,080 --> 00:05:55,680
I've interrogated them.

149
00:05:56,910 --> 00:05:58,000
These people

150
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,680
are not unruly mobs

151
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,760
acting out of malice

152
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:03,560
but are being manipulated from behind,

153
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:06,230
aiming to slander your reputation.

154
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:07,600
Your Highness,

155
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:09,590
guess who this person is.

156
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:14,640
You wouldn't have guessed.

157
00:06:22,710 --> 00:06:25,000
The person behind this wicked plot

158
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:28,000
is your younger sister,

159
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:30,350
Princess Lin'an.

160
00:06:36,150 --> 00:06:37,390
I feel ashamed to say it,

161
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:40,640
but I've also uncovered the motive
behind this crime.

162
00:06:41,230 --> 00:06:42,680
Princess Lin'an

163
00:06:44,270 --> 00:06:45,710
wants to recruit me.

164
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,150
What do you think?

165
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:51,710
Your Highness,

166
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:53,350
I don't need to think.

167
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:56,590
Though Princess Lin'an
wants to recruit me,

168
00:06:56,790 --> 00:06:58,680
she probably doesn't understand
my character.

169
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:01,390
Otherwise, she wouldn't have resorted
to such methods,

170
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:05,520
and she wouldn't know that I'm loyal
and don't serve two masters.

171
00:07:06,470 --> 00:07:08,560
Don't be so absolute in your words.

172
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:10,350
Lin'an went

173
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:12,080
through so much trouble.

174
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:14,470
She must be genuinely trying
to recruit you.

175
00:07:15,710 --> 00:07:17,220
How about giving it a second thought?

176
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:19,760
I understand now.

177
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:21,030
You understand again?

178
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:23,790
I understand the reason
you tested me earlier.

179
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:27,080
Your Highness, you are

180
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:29,150
truly brilliant

181
00:07:29,150 --> 00:07:30,590
and well-informed.

182
00:07:30,710 --> 00:07:34,120
You knew Princess Lin'an
wanted to recruit me,

183
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:36,710
so you deliberately tested me

184
00:07:36,910 --> 00:07:38,790
to see if I would seek another master.

185
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,910
You figured it all out?

186
00:07:44,390 --> 00:07:45,560
Rest assured, Your Highness.

187
00:07:45,710 --> 00:07:47,200
I am willing to prove my loyalty

188
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,640
with action.

189
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:51,030
I will take these rogues
back to the yamen and punish them.

190
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:52,480
No need for that.

191
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:57,710
I already know your loyalty,

192
00:07:58,320 --> 00:08:00,350
but this is quite suspicious.

193
00:08:00,470 --> 00:08:02,030
I need to personally interrogate them.

194
00:08:02,350 --> 00:08:03,190
Xuan,

195
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:05,000
keep an eye on them.

196
00:08:05,790 --> 00:08:06,630
As for you,

197
00:08:07,230 --> 00:08:09,000
you can go on with your business.

198
00:08:09,830 --> 00:08:12,150
Alright then, I will take my leave.

199
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,520
Xuan.

200
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:15,870
- Don't let them harm the princess.
- Sure.

201
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:16,310
Alright.

202
00:08:19,710 --> 00:08:20,680
Take care.

203
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:26,580
Are you alright?

204
00:08:26,790 --> 00:08:28,030
What's wrong with you?

205
00:08:28,030 --> 00:08:29,320
How did you get caught?

206
00:08:29,390 --> 00:08:32,200
At first, we followed the orders

207
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:34,470
and swore it was all Huaiqing's doing.

208
00:08:34,590 --> 00:08:35,560
But who would've known

209
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:37,280
Mr. Xu knows

210
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:39,630
a Master from the Academy?

211
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,750
(Heart Spell)
A gentleman must be sincere,

212
00:08:41,750 --> 00:08:43,060
and so must an ordinary person.

213
00:08:43,590 --> 00:08:45,080
Before meeting the Master,

214
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,920
we still stuck to the same answer.

215
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:48,080
But who would've thought

216
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,680
they'd use the Heart Spell on us?

217
00:08:49,830 --> 00:08:53,080
We were even beaten.

218
00:08:54,110 --> 00:08:56,870
Our bodies and minds
suffered double torture.

219
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:59,350
Your Highness, we really had no choice.

220
00:08:59,870 --> 00:09:00,800
Alright, alright.

221
00:09:01,630 --> 00:09:03,750
Xuan, give them each 20 liang

222
00:09:03,750 --> 00:09:04,920
and let them go home.

223
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,800
Alright.

224
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:08,590
Thank you, Your Highness.

225
00:09:08,590 --> 00:09:09,940
Please.

226
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:11,800
Take care.

227
00:09:11,830 --> 00:09:12,870
Sorry.

228
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,230
Your Highness.

229
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:23,750
What should we do?

230
00:09:24,630 --> 00:09:27,320
I didn't expect Mr. Xu to be so clever.

231
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:29,080
Did we just

232
00:09:29,510 --> 00:09:32,160
lose more than we gained?

233
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:41,110
Even I'm moved to hear this,

234
00:09:41,350 --> 00:09:44,110
let alone the Grand Princess.

235
00:09:44,350 --> 00:09:47,350
She was indeed greatly shocked.

236
00:09:48,800 --> 00:09:50,680
Are you saying Huaiqing

237
00:09:50,680 --> 00:09:52,320
was wary of you back then?

238
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,320
She did.

239
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:56,510
She had tested me with words before.

240
00:09:56,510 --> 00:09:58,280
I was confused for quite a while.

241
00:09:58,280 --> 00:10:00,750
It's perfect
that Lin'an came right to me.

242
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:02,920
I took this chance to show my loyalty.

243
00:10:03,470 --> 00:10:06,040
Now, the Grand Princess
must trust you completely, right?

244
00:10:06,230 --> 00:10:07,750
Not just the Grand Princess.

245
00:10:10,230 --> 00:10:11,870
Yesterday, I also did a good job

246
00:10:11,990 --> 00:10:13,200
in front of Lord Wei,

247
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:14,960
and now

248
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,470
he trusts me quite a lot.

249
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:21,750
Two major patrons in one day.

250
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,040
Ningyan,

251
00:10:23,870 --> 00:10:25,040
thanks to you,

252
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:29,510
our family's glory and wealth
are just around the corner.

253
00:10:31,470 --> 00:10:32,870
Uncle, you're too kind.

254
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:35,280
I still have a lot to learn from you.

255
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:37,560
After all,
when it comes to serving others,

256
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:38,960
you have more experience.

257
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:39,990
No, no, no.

258
00:10:40,280 --> 00:10:42,230
The student has surpassed the teacher.

259
00:10:42,230 --> 00:10:44,470
You're on the verge of surpassing me.

260
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:45,920
You taught me

261
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:47,590
all my martial arts skills, Uncle.

262
00:10:47,590 --> 00:10:48,450
No, no, no.

263
00:10:48,450 --> 00:10:49,830
The younger generation

264
00:10:49,830 --> 00:10:50,990
surpasses the older.

265
00:10:50,990 --> 00:10:52,160
No, no, no.

266
00:10:52,160 --> 00:10:53,960
You'll always be my uncle.

267
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,560
No, no, no. The world is yours,

268
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:56,590
and the future is yours.

269
00:10:56,590 --> 00:10:57,800
Everything is yours.

270
00:10:57,800 --> 00:10:59,440
Without you, where would we be?

271
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,510
Uncle, I'll kowtow to you.

272
00:11:00,510 --> 00:11:02,870
Please don't be modest, Ningyan.

273
00:11:02,870 --> 00:11:05,440
- No, no. I'll kowtow to you.
- I'll kowtow to you.

274
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:06,710
No, no, no.

275
00:11:11,140 --> 00:11:13,300
(Guardians)

276
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:27,230
Mr. Tao.

277
00:11:27,350 --> 00:11:28,190
