556
00:25:11,230 --> 00:25:12,640
That's even worse.

557
00:25:13,070 --> 00:25:15,640
First, I'd offend Mr. Yang,

558
00:25:15,750 --> 00:25:16,960
and with Mr. Jiang,

559
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:19,990
I'd just be a petty person
who changes sides.

560
00:25:20,070 --> 00:25:21,470
After this,

561
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:23,200
he'll never trust me completely.

562
00:25:23,200 --> 00:25:24,880
It'll be uncomfortable.

563
00:25:25,710 --> 00:25:26,640
Makes sense.

564
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:30,920
So, you're really not choosing anyone?

565
00:25:32,070 --> 00:25:33,680
Of course, I'll choose.

566
00:25:34,030 --> 00:25:35,030
But,

567
00:25:35,750 --> 00:25:38,510
I'll need someone else to choose for me.

568
00:25:38,750 --> 00:25:40,010
Choose for you?

569
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:41,240
Choose for you?

570
00:25:41,470 --> 00:25:43,840
What does that mean?

571
00:25:48,750 --> 00:25:49,710
Who won?

572
00:25:49,880 --> 00:25:51,160
- I won.
- I won.

573
00:25:56,270 --> 00:25:58,510
If I hadn't reined in my breath,

574
00:25:58,510 --> 00:26:00,120
you wouldn't have lasted ten rounds.

575
00:26:00,120 --> 00:26:01,990
If I used my spear,

576
00:26:02,360 --> 00:26:04,310
you wouldn't have lasted one round.

577
00:26:05,310 --> 00:26:07,230
Talking big, huh?

578
00:26:07,870 --> 00:26:08,990
Want to give it another try?

579
00:26:08,990 --> 00:26:10,030
Sure, let's try.

580
00:26:10,030 --> 00:26:11,440
- Alright.
- Yang Yan.

581
00:26:12,230 --> 00:26:13,070
Yes.

582
00:26:13,360 --> 00:26:14,200
Serve the tea.

583
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:17,280
Yes.

584
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:34,200
Xu Qi'an said

585
00:26:35,750 --> 00:26:37,230
that about the transfer,

586
00:26:38,120 --> 00:26:40,200
he had his own thoughts.

587
00:26:41,120 --> 00:26:42,270
What did he say?

588
00:26:44,750 --> 00:26:47,120
With what I know about the Gold Gongs,

589
00:26:47,360 --> 00:26:49,400
I can't make
the most correct choice now.

590
00:26:49,680 --> 00:26:50,790
What's so hard about it?

591
00:26:51,510 --> 00:26:52,850
If you want better martial arts,

592
00:26:52,960 --> 00:26:53,880
choose Yang Yan.

593
00:26:54,880 --> 00:26:56,270
If you want a better physique,

594
00:26:57,030 --> 00:26:59,360
Jiang Lyuzhong is your best choice.

595
00:27:00,640 --> 00:27:01,780
I don't favor martial arts.

596
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:03,400
Or rather, as a Guardian,

597
00:27:03,790 --> 00:27:05,160
what I pursue is not

598
00:27:05,440 --> 00:27:07,030
the absolute level of martial power.

599
00:27:07,470 --> 00:27:08,400
Then what is it?

600
00:27:10,120 --> 00:27:11,400
Lord Wei, do you still remember

601
00:27:12,470 --> 00:27:14,120
why you rated me as A+?

602
00:27:15,920 --> 00:27:17,710
Our little Copper Gong said

603
00:27:17,990 --> 00:27:18,990
this poem represented

604
00:27:19,060 --> 00:27:21,230
(You live off the people's resources.)
what he wants.

605
00:27:21,230 --> 00:27:22,740
(You can't fool the heavens.)

606
00:27:23,070 --> 00:27:25,200
You let Lord Wei choose for you?

607
00:27:25,550 --> 00:27:26,390
That's right.

608
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:28,880
Since either choice is wrong,

609
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:30,680
it's better to stay quiet

610
00:27:30,880 --> 00:27:34,470
and give the choice to Lord Wei.

611
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:39,640
Then why did you write that poem?

612
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:40,960
Wasn't that unnecessary?

613
00:27:41,160 --> 00:27:42,310
You don't understand.

614
00:27:42,880 --> 00:27:45,400
If I had started
by suggesting Lord Wei choose,

615
00:27:45,790 --> 00:27:48,030
it'd have left a bad impression,

616
00:27:48,200 --> 00:27:49,990
as if I were timid and indecisive.

617
00:27:50,310 --> 00:27:52,200
But if I presented that poem,

618
00:27:52,200 --> 00:27:53,040
first,

619
00:27:53,070 --> 00:27:55,200
it would show that my stance is clear

620
00:27:55,200 --> 00:27:57,600
that I am a Guardian with integrity.

621
00:27:57,920 --> 00:28:00,070
Second, it allows me
to express my aspirations,

622
00:28:00,470 --> 00:28:02,680
which brings me closer to Lord Wei.

623
00:28:02,960 --> 00:28:03,800
After all,

624
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:06,310
he must have liked the poem,

625
00:28:06,510 --> 00:28:09,360
so he rated me as A+.

626
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:27,510
Brilliant! Brilliant!

627
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:29,550
Brilliant!

628
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:32,840
Xu Qi'an, you're hitting two birds
with one stone.

629
00:28:33,470 --> 00:28:35,060
Xu Qi'an, come and let me take a look.

630
00:28:35,160 --> 00:28:36,640
No, I'll come over to check.

631
00:28:36,790 --> 00:28:38,080
I'll come over to look at you.

632
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:40,550
I'll go check if you have
a hundred cunning schemes.

633
00:28:40,550 --> 00:28:41,790
Go away.

634
00:28:42,510 --> 00:28:44,200
This is nothing.

635
00:28:45,310 --> 00:28:48,880
Mastering the preferences
of your superior

636
00:28:48,990 --> 00:28:51,400
is a fundamental skill for every worker.

637
00:28:51,960 --> 00:28:52,990
Worker?

638
00:28:53,360 --> 00:28:54,200
Guardian.

639
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:57,270
Clever.

640
00:28:57,960 --> 00:29:01,160
Lord Wei will surely choose
the best Gold Gong for you.

641
00:29:03,470 --> 00:29:04,310
Well.

642
00:29:05,840 --> 00:29:09,310
Can you help us get assigned over there?

643
00:29:10,070 --> 00:29:11,360
You two want a transfer?

644
00:29:12,640 --> 00:29:14,640
Gold Gongs
are better than Silver Gongs.

645
00:29:20,230 --> 00:29:21,070
Mr. Xu,

646
00:29:21,230 --> 00:29:22,840
Lord Wei's Transfer Order has arrived.

647
00:29:23,160 --> 00:29:25,440
Who has Lord Wei assigned him to?

648
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:26,280
I don't know.

649
00:29:26,470 --> 00:29:28,070
Mr. Li asked you to go over there.

650
00:29:31,600 --> 00:29:32,440
Make way.

651
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:33,520
Move.

652
00:29:34,360 --> 00:29:35,920
Clear this way.

653
00:29:37,640 --> 00:29:40,400
Mr. Xu is leaving.

654
00:29:41,230 --> 00:29:42,070
Applause.

655
00:30:09,360 --> 00:30:10,200
Chief.

656
00:30:12,230 --> 00:30:13,510
Is this really your decision?

657
00:30:15,640 --> 00:30:16,480
Well.

658
00:30:18,030 --> 00:30:19,440
It's Lord Wei's decision.

659
00:30:21,840 --> 00:30:23,600
I heard you went to Haoqi Tower.

660
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:25,960
Wasn't that your choice?

661
00:30:26,360 --> 00:30:27,270
Of course not.

662
00:30:28,030 --> 00:30:29,840
I'm just a small Copper Gong.

663
00:30:30,440 --> 00:30:31,880
I don't have the right to choose.

664
00:30:34,750 --> 00:30:36,440
But I still argued my case

665
00:30:36,990 --> 00:30:38,470
and bravely asked Lord Wei

666
00:30:38,840 --> 00:30:40,790
if I could stay at Breeze Hall

667
00:30:40,790 --> 00:30:43,230
and if I could stay under your command.

668
00:30:43,550 --> 00:30:44,880
Stay under my command?

669
00:30:57,960 --> 00:30:58,800
Chief,

670
00:31:01,440 --> 00:31:02,280
honestly,

671
00:31:03,400 --> 00:31:04,750
at first, I wanted to leave.

672
00:31:06,440 --> 00:31:08,710
But after spending this time together,

673
00:31:10,750 --> 00:31:12,030
I've already considered myself

674
00:31:13,120 --> 00:31:14,990
a member of Breeze Hall.

675
00:31:19,790 --> 00:31:21,680
When I entered this room,

676
00:31:21,680 --> 00:31:22,640
I thought so.

677
00:31:23,710 --> 00:31:25,030
When out on cases,

678
00:31:25,790 --> 00:31:26,990
I still thought so.

679
00:31:43,550 --> 00:31:44,470
Although

680
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:48,120
you still have
some misunderstandings about me,

681
00:31:49,520 --> 00:31:50,800
I genuinely want

682
00:31:51,990 --> 00:31:54,200
to stay at Breeze Hall.

683
00:31:56,440 --> 00:31:57,750
So, what did Lord Wei say?

684
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:03,230
Lord Wei found it strange.

685
00:32:11,120 --> 00:32:12,400
You chose me, a Silver Gong,

686
00:32:12,880 --> 00:32:14,200
instead of a Gold Gong.

687
00:32:15,680 --> 00:32:17,310
Anyone would find that strange.

688
00:32:17,310 --> 00:32:18,550
That's just prejudice.

689
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:20,710
Gold Gongs and Silver Gongs

690
00:32:20,990 --> 00:32:22,230
are all Guardians.

691
00:32:22,550 --> 00:32:24,030
We all serve the people.

692
00:32:24,440 --> 00:32:26,120
What's so superior or inferior
about that?

693
00:32:26,550 --> 00:32:27,510
Do you really think so?

694
00:32:27,510 --> 00:32:29,230
I've always thought so.

695
00:32:33,600 --> 00:32:35,840
It's a pity that my opinion alone
doesn't matter.

696
00:32:37,160 --> 00:32:38,000
Who am I?

697
00:32:39,120 --> 00:32:41,360
I'm just a small Copper Gong.

698
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:44,640
My words are insignificant.

699
00:32:45,790 --> 00:32:47,680
In the end,
Lord Wei didn't take me seriously.

700
00:32:53,470 --> 00:32:54,310
Chief,

701
00:32:55,200 --> 00:32:56,600
I owe you this.

702
00:32:57,160 --> 00:32:58,990
If there's ever anything needed
in the hall,

703
00:32:59,120 --> 00:33:00,360
I will

704
00:33:00,680 --> 00:33:01,920
risk my life

705
00:33:02,030 --> 00:33:02,990
for you.

706
00:33:03,070 --> 00:33:03,960
No, Ningyan.

707
00:33:04,480 --> 00:33:05,530
There's no need for that.

708
00:33:05,540 --> 00:33:06,640
There must be.

709
00:33:06,920 --> 00:33:08,200
One day at Breeze Hall

710
00:33:08,600 --> 00:33:09,840
is enough to make it forever.

711
00:33:12,200 --> 00:33:13,990
Wherever Lord Wei
assigns me in the future,

712
00:33:14,960 --> 00:33:15,800
my heart

713
00:33:16,710 --> 00:33:18,310
will always stay with you, Chief.

714
00:33:19,070 --> 00:33:21,200
It'll always stay at Breeze Hall.

715
00:33:26,920 --> 00:33:28,070
With your words,

716
00:33:30,120 --> 00:33:31,230
I am content.

717
00:33:34,750 --> 00:33:36,120
I'll go get your Transfer Order.

718
00:34:00,070 --> 00:34:00,910
Your Transfer Order.

719
00:34:04,990 --> 00:34:06,470
Is it appropriate to look at it here?

720
00:34:13,980 --> 00:34:16,140
(Transfer Order)

721
00:34:17,980 --> 00:34:20,500
(For the next three years,
Xu Qi'an will stay at Breeze Hall)

722
00:34:20,500 --> 00:34:21,660
(under Li Yuchun's command.)

723
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:24,990
Didn't expect it, did you?

724
00:34:25,150 --> 00:34:27,190
You persuaded Lord Wei!

725
00:34:38,800 --> 00:34:39,670
Ningyan, you...

726
00:34:40,030 --> 00:34:41,400
What's wrong?

727
00:34:43,440 --> 00:34:44,630
It's nothing, bro.

728
00:34:45,510 --> 00:34:46,510
I'm just too excited.

729
00:34:53,720 --> 00:34:55,720
Lord Wei really assigned me to you?

730
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:57,320
Lord Wei wrote this Transfer Order.

731
00:34:57,320 --> 00:34:58,590
No one can change it.

732
00:35:00,030 --> 00:35:00,960
No one can change it?

733
00:35:03,240 --> 00:35:04,080
Don't worry.

734
00:35:04,150 --> 00:35:05,400
Not only can it not be changed,

735
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:07,190
but to prevent others
from taking you away,

736
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:09,880
Lord Wei specifically added
a time limit:

737
00:35:10,190 --> 00:35:11,030
Three years.

738
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:13,190
For the next three years,
you'll stay with me,

739
00:35:13,190 --> 00:35:14,800
and there will be no personnel changes.

740
00:35:15,740 --> 00:35:16,740
(Transfer Order)

741
00:35:22,590 --> 00:35:23,440
Three years.

742
00:35:32,630 --> 00:35:33,760
Li Yuchun?

743
00:35:33,960 --> 00:35:35,840
So, he's still
under Yang Yan's command?

744
00:35:36,240 --> 00:35:39,150
Lord Wei, although Yang Yan
is your adopted son,

745
00:35:39,150 --> 00:35:41,110
you still can't be
so biased towards him.

746
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:42,640
How insolent!

747
00:35:46,760 --> 00:35:47,630
How long has it been?

748
00:35:48,670 --> 00:35:49,590
Quite a while.

749
00:35:50,990 --> 00:35:53,320
It must be hard for the chief
to accept it.

750
00:35:53,630 --> 00:35:54,990
After all, he's an A+.

751
00:35:58,240 --> 00:35:59,470
These past few days,

752
00:35:59,470 --> 00:36:00,920
he'll surely be upset.

753
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:03,150
We should hold off

754
00:36:03,280 --> 00:36:04,510
on the transfer for now.

755
00:36:07,100 --> 00:36:08,750
I'm a bit reluctant to leave the chief.

756
00:36:09,590 --> 00:36:11,470
People strive for higher positions,

757
00:36:11,470 --> 00:36:13,240
and water flows to lower places, right?

758
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:15,070
Well, with this development,

759
00:36:15,070 --> 00:36:16,590
I'll be Gold Gong Song,

760
00:36:16,720 --> 00:36:17,590
and you'll be

761
00:36:17,990 --> 00:36:18,990
Silver Gong Zhu.

762
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:20,680
That's right.

763
00:36:20,720 --> 00:36:22,800
Every banquet ends.

764
00:36:24,110 --> 00:36:26,150
Let's invite him
to the Imperial Office of Music.

765
00:36:26,150 --> 00:36:27,070
Who? The chief?

766
00:36:31,670 --> 00:36:32,960
Why are you still sitting there?

767
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:33,800
- No.
- Come here.

768
00:36:34,510 --> 00:36:35,470
Did I see it wrong?

769
00:36:35,470 --> 00:36:36,400
Why is he smiling?

770
00:36:37,440 --> 00:36:39,070
He's just acting tough.

771
00:36:39,280 --> 00:36:40,470
Then it's settled.

772
00:36:40,720 --> 00:36:42,590
(Breeze Hall)
We'll call each other brothers.

773
00:36:42,880 --> 00:36:44,190
Anyone who dares to bully you

774
00:36:44,440 --> 00:36:46,110
is bullying Breeze Hall.

775
00:36:46,110 --> 00:36:47,150
I'll never let them off.

776
00:36:49,190 --> 00:36:50,240
Call each other brothers?

777
00:36:51,880 --> 00:36:53,590
Just his final plea for him to stay.

778
00:36:53,760 --> 00:36:55,070
From now on, work hard with me.

779
00:36:55,070 --> 00:36:56,880
I'll train you with all my might.

780
00:36:56,990 --> 00:36:57,830
What?

781
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:58,920
Work hard?

782
00:37:00,020 --> 00:37:01,400
His final...

783
00:37:03,760 --> 00:37:05,290
Why are you two still sitting there?

784
00:37:05,470 --> 00:37:06,310
Get to work.

785
00:37:06,320 --> 00:37:07,160
Alright.

786
00:37:13,590 --> 00:37:15,070
Later, pick a place,

787
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:16,760
and we'll have a good drink.

788
00:37:16,880 --> 00:37:17,720
My treat.

789
00:37:18,190 --> 00:37:19,030
Yes, Chief.

790
00:37:20,400 --> 00:37:21,440
What did you just call me?

791
00:37:23,030 --> 00:37:23,870
Yuchun.

792
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:27,680
Yuchun.

793
00:37:28,990 --> 00:37:30,280
Right.

794
00:37:34,800 --> 00:37:35,640
Ningyan.

795
00:37:36,700 --> 00:37:37,590
Ningyan.

796
00:37:37,590 --> 00:37:38,590
(Breeze Hall)

797
00:37:38,590 --> 00:37:39,470
What's going on?

798
00:37:39,630 --> 00:37:40,630
Did I hear that wrong?

799
00:37:41,320 --> 00:37:42,630
What's going on?

800
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:45,470
I want to know what's going on too.

801
00:37:48,630 --> 00:37:49,470
Let's go.

802
00:37:50,030 --> 00:37:50,870
Gold Gong Song.

803
00:37:51,510 --> 00:37:53,350
Do I still have a chance to be
a Gold Gong?

804
00:38:01,280 --> 00:38:04,360
Actually, I think
it's nice to stay with us...

805
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:06,120
How about

806
00:38:06,150 --> 00:38:07,070
we go drink?

807
00:38:07,990 --> 00:38:09,590
I just want to be quiet for a while.

808
00:38:14,660 --> 00:38:18,820
(Go Straight)

809
00:38:24,590 --> 00:38:25,670
Lord Wei, please calm down.

810
00:38:25,670 --> 00:38:26,920
I spoke out of turn.

811
00:38:27,360 --> 00:38:28,760
Since you have made a decision,

812
00:38:28,760 --> 00:38:29,600
I will

813
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:31,150
follow your orders.

814
00:38:32,110 --> 00:38:32,990
But

815
00:38:33,400 --> 00:38:34,960
may I ask

816
00:38:36,150 --> 00:38:38,320
why you chose Li Yuchun?

817
00:38:39,550 --> 00:38:41,150
Xu Qi'an is quick-witted

818
00:38:41,400 --> 00:38:42,960
and doesn't follow rigid rules

819
00:38:42,960 --> 00:38:45,150
but his own heart.

820
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:47,080
Therefore,

821
00:38:47,760 --> 00:38:50,670
he needs a rigid and disciplined person
as a superior.

822
00:38:51,920 --> 00:38:53,840
Li Yuchun is a person

823
00:38:55,320 --> 00:38:56,840
who won't tolerate anything amiss.

824
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:58,880
If it were any one of you,

825
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:01,510
you'd have had conflicts with him.

826
00:39:01,800 --> 00:39:03,150
That may be true,

827
00:39:03,590 --> 00:39:06,590
but Li Yuchun is just a Silver Gong.

828
00:39:07,030 --> 00:39:08,840
How could Xu Qi'an
be willing to follow him?

829
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:12,840
He will.

830
00:39:16,470 --> 00:39:17,100
They

831
00:39:17,100 --> 00:39:18,700
(You live off the people's resources.)

832
00:39:18,700 --> 00:39:20,580
(You can't fool the heavens.)
are like-minded.

833
00:39:24,110 --> 00:39:25,630
Since you've chosen me,

834
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:28,760
you must do things my way.

835
00:39:29,360 --> 00:39:30,960
As a Guardian,

836
00:39:31,880 --> 00:39:33,560
you cannot take bribes
or pervert the law.

837
00:39:33,630 --> 00:39:35,150
You cannot disrespect your superiors,

